verses.text:
What a day of trial shall be, When the Lord shall try;
When that day of trial shall be, When the saints shall fly;
When that day of trial shall be, When the Lord shall come;
When that day of trial shall be, He shall judge each one.

What a day of trial shall be, When the Lord shall try;
When that day of trial shall be, We shall hear the cry;
When that day of trial shall be, When the Lord shall come;
When that day of trial shall be, He shall judge each one.

What a day of trial shall be, When the Lord shall try;
When that day of trial shall be, When the saints shall fly;
When that day of trial shall be, When the Lord shall come;
When that day of trial shall be, He shall judge each one.
